                              a.faq__store__link(href='https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.instaprotek.app&hl=en_US', target='_blank', title='Get it on Google Play') 
                                img(src='/imgs/download_google_play.png', alt='Get it on Google Play')
                          li.faq__list__item
                            a.faq__list__item--question(href='#faq') What is the step by step process of registration using the app? 
                            .faq__list__item--answer
                              p Registration is easy on the app. See our video below for the step by step process.
                              .faq__video.vertical_video
                                p Android
                                video(id='my-video', class='video-js', controls, preload='auto', data-setup='{"aspectRatio":"16:9"}', poster='./imgs/instaprotek_video_poster.jpg')
                                  source(src='./instaprotek_Android_Video_STEPS_09_11_19.mp4', type='video/mp4')
                                  p(class='vjs-no-js') To view this video please enable JavaScript, and consider upgrading to a web browser that
                              .faq__video.vertical_video
