                          li.faq__list__item
                            a.faq__list__item--question(href='#faq') What is the purchase receipt being asked to be uploaded? Is it for my device?
                            .faq__list__item--answer
                              p The purchase receipt is pertaining to the screen protection you have purchased and not for the device.
                          li.faq__list__item
                            a.faq__list__item--question(href='#faq') I am having trouble with the app during the registration, what can I do?
                            .faq__list__item--answer
                              p Give us a call right away at 
                                |
                                span.text--bold (888) 908-2078 
                                | or email us at 
                                a(href='mailto:support@instaprotek.com') support@instaprotek.com
                          

                      .faq__group
                        h3.faq__group__title Claim Process
                        ol.faq__list
                          li.faq__list__item
                            a.faq__list__item--question(href='#faq') How can I file a claim?
                            .faq__list__item--answer
                              p You can easily file a claim using the app. Just log-in to your account and click on FILE A CLAIM. You can also do it online by going to 
                                |
                                a(href='//register.instaprotek.com/myaccount', target='_blank') register.instaprotek.com/myaccount 
                                | or you can simply give us a call and our friendly representatives will be happy to help you in filing a claim. You can reach us at 
                                span.text--bold (888) 908-2078 
                                | or email us at 
                                a(href='mailto:support@instaprotek.com') support@instaprotek.com
                              .faq__video
                                video(id='my-video', class='video-js', controls, preload='auto', data-setup='{"aspectRatio":"16:9"}', poster='./imgs/warranty/video_poster.jpg')
                                  source(src='./instaprotek_File_a_Claim_STEPS_09_09_19.mp4', type='video/mp4')
                                  p(class='vjs-no-js') To view this video please enable JavaScript, and consider upgrading to a web browser that
                          li.faq__list__item
                            a.faq__list__item--question(href='#faq') What is the claims process?
                            .faq__list__item--answer
                              p Once you have submitted a claim via our app, online or over a call with our representative, you have a maximum of 30 days to have your device fixed at any repair center or you can use your existing phone insurance for a replacement if your phone is beyond repair.
                              p When you already have your receipt from the repair center or your confirmation email and receipt from your insurance company, you need to take a photo of it and upload it using your app or online. Or you can simply email the receipt to claims@instaprotek.com with your claim number as the subject line. 
                              p After we receive it, we will then validate the receipt with the repair center or the insurance company. Once validated, the status will change to approve and we will have our claims team process the reimbursement.
                              p Reimbursement will take a maximum of 10 banking days and will be sent to the address we have on your account.
                              p You will be notified via email once the reimbursement will be mailed to you.
                          li.faq__list__item
                            a.faq__list__item--question(href='#faq') How much would be my coverage amount?
                            .faq__list__item--answer
                              p It depends on the product you have purchased however, we only have 2 amounts available -- $100 and $250. This would show on your account once you register or at the back of the product packaging you have purchased.
                      
                      
                      .faq__group
                        h3.faq__group__title Troubleshooting
                        ol.faq__list
                          li.faq__list__item
                            a.faq__list__item--question(href='#faq') Can’t proceed with the screen test?
                            .faq__list__item--answer
                              p Check if there are unfilled areas on your screen.
                              p If there are, slide your fingers on your phone’s screen continuously until you fully fill them up.
                              .faq__video.vertical_video
                                //- p Android
                                video(id='my-video', class='video-js', controls, preload='auto', data-setup='{"aspectRatio":"16:9"}', poster='./imgs/instaprotek_video_poster.jpg')
                                  source(src='./instaprotek_How to Screen Swiping.mp4', type='video/mp4')
                                  p(class='vjs-no-js') To view this video please enable JavaScript, and consider upgrading to a web browser that
                          li.faq__list__item
                            a.faq__list__item--question(href='#faq') Can’t proceed with the PIN verification?
                            .faq__list__item--answer
                              p Check the validity of your PIN.
                              p If your PIN is invalid or expired, contact customer support at 
                                |
                                span.text--bold (888) 908-2078 
                                | for assistance.
                          li.faq__list__item
                            a.faq__list__item--question(href='#faq') If you’re unable to install the InstaProtek app, follow these steps:
                            .faq__list__item--answer
                              .sublist
                                .sublist__item Go to your phone’s 
                                  | 
                                  span.text--bold(style='margin: 0 0.25rem;') “Settings” 
                                .sublist__item
                                  | Tap 
                                  span.text--bold(style='margin: 0 0.25rem;') "Apps"
                                .sublist__item 
                                  | Scroll down and tap 
                                  span.text--bold(style='margin: 0 0.25rem;') “Google Play Store” 
                                .sublist__item 
                                  | Tap 
                                  span.text--bold(style='margin: 0 0.25rem;') “Storage” 
                                  | and tap 
                                  span.text--bold(style='margin: 0 0.25rem;') “Clear cache” 
                                  | and 
                                  span.text--bold(style='margin: 0 0.25rem;') “Clear data” 
                                .sublist__item Open Google Play Store again and redownload the InstaProtek App

                              .faq__video.vertical_video
                                p Android
                                video(id='my-video', class='video-js', controls, preload='auto', data-setup='{"aspectRatio":"16:9"}', poster='./imgs/instaprotek_video_poster.jpg')
                                  source(src='./instaprotek_Trouble Shooting Steps.mp4', type='video/mp4')
                                  p(class='vjs-no-js') To view this video please enable JavaScript, and consider upgrading to a web browser that


              .step__footer
                a.backtop.btn-floating.btn-large.waves-effect.waves-light.red(href='#backtotop')
                  i.material-icons keyboard_arrow_up